# This group is a fake group used to have all the hosts
# on coreos use the same vars
# Some hosts are referenced using differents hostnames
# So some secondary hostnames used to reference a coreos host
# are not in the "coreos" group (as it would run twice the roles for the same host)
# So this group is here to take care of sharing the coreos hosts config.
